                        "description": "Get all points for the authenticated user with various filters.\n\n**Authentication:** Required (Bearer token)\n\n**Query Parameters (all optional):**\n- `status`: Filter by status (available/used/expired)\n- `order_id`: Filter by order ID\n- `product_id`: Filter by product ID\n- `date_from`: Filter from date (YYYY-MM-DD)\n- `date_to`: Filter to date (YYYY-MM-DD)\n- `expired_only`: Show only expired points\n- `expiring_within_days`: Show points expiring within X days\n- `per_page`: Number of items per page (default: 15)\n\n**Response includes:**\n- Paginated list of points\n- Each point includes: id, points_count, status, expire_at, used_at, description, order info, product info, timestamps"
                    },
