                        "description": "Preview order calculation before creating the actual order. This endpoint calculates all costs, discounts, shipping, tax, and points discount based on cart items.\n\n**Authentication:** Required (Bearer token)\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `payment_method_id` (required): Payment method ID\n- `delivery_method` (required): Delivery method - 'home_delivery' or 'store_pickup'\n- `location_id` (required if delivery_method is 'home_delivery'): Location/address ID\n- `discount_code` (optional): Discount code to apply\n- `use_point` (optional): Boolean - true to use available points for discount\n\n**Response includes:**\n- Items: Cart items with product details\n- Summary: subtotal, discount, shipping, tax, payment method fee, points discount, total\n- Shipping info: City details, location, free shipping threshold\n- Payment method details\n- Points info: Available points, points to use, discount amount\n- Warnings: Stock issues, inactive payment methods\n- Settings: Tax percentage, free shipping threshold, point value"
